Description:
    Initializes a Rails application to use jspec-rails.

Examples:
    `./script/generate jspec_init`

        creates the following files
                         jspec
                         jspec/fixtures
                         jspec/spec
       JSpec Test View:  jspec/spec/index.html.erb
           Sample Spec:  jspec/spec/jspec_rails_spec.js
        Sample Fixture:  jspec/fixtures/test_fixture.html.erb
                Config:  jspec/jspec.yml

        adds the JSpec javascript library to your public dir:
                         public/jspec
                         public/jspec/jspec.js
                         public/jspec/jspec.jquery.js
                         public/jspec/jspec.css
                         public/jspec/images
                         public/jspec/images/bg.png
                         public/jspec/images/hr.png
                         public/jspec/images/sprites.bg.png
                         public/jspec/images/sprites.png
                         public/jspec/images/vr.png
                        
            
            
